javafx.scene.control

Class TableColumn.CellDataFeatures<S,T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.control.TableColumn.CellDataFeatures<S,T>
  • Type Parameters:
    S - The TableView type
    T - The TableColumn type
    Enclosing class:
    TableColumn<S,T>

    public static class TableColumn.CellDataFeatures<S,T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A support class used in TableColumn as a wrapper class to provide all necessary information for a particular Cell. Once instantiated, this class is immutable.
